# NexEV Private Limited

> Driven by Electric Future

NexEV is an early-stage Indian electric vehicle (EV) company incorporated in Karnataka, India. The company supplies 18650 lithium-ion battery assembly kits, EV components, and sourced battery management systems (BMS) to EV workshops, hobbyists, and dealers across India. Business activities span manufacturing (battery pack assembly), trading (component import and resale), service (workshop technical support and after-sales), and distribution (dealer and wholesale supply chain).

