## Current Business (Phase 1 — Active)

NexEV currently sells **18650 DIY battery pack assembly kits** via Amazon India and direct orders to EV workshops and hobbyists. Each kit contains all components required to assemble a lithium-ion battery pack:

| Component | Specification |
|---|---|
| Nickel strip | High-purity, for cell-to-cell spot welding |
| 14 AWG silicone wire | Red and black, heat-resistant, flexible |
| PVC heat shrink tube | Blue, 170mm flat width |
| Kapton tape | Polyimide, 25mm width, 200 per roll |
| 18650 insulation rings | Cell-end positive terminal insulation |
| Insulation paper roll | Between-cell group insulation |
| Amass XT60H connectors | Male + female, gold-plated, genuine Amass |
| 80650 battery holders | Plastic, for cell alignment during welding |

Kits are used for e-bike battery builds, power tool packs, solar storage, and EV conversion projects.

