## India BIS Compliance Context

BIS (Bureau of Indian Standards) certification is **mandatory** for the following EV components to be legally sold in India:

| Component | BIS Standard |
|---|---|
| Battery cells and packs | IS 16046 |
| Battery Management System (BMS) | IS 16893 |
| EV chargers | IS 16170 |
| Motor controllers | IS 17017 |
| BLDC motors | IS 16171 |

NexEV can support BIS compliance registration for supply partner products entering the Indian market.

